	(11, 10, 'OES_GUI_DEV', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<pre class="prettyprint lang-bsh">################SETENVIRONMENT VARIABLE################\r\nexportJAVA_HOME=/usr/java/jdk1.7.0_21\r\nexportM2_HOME=/usr/local/maven/apache-maven-3.0.3\r\nexportAUTO_HOME=${WORKSPACE}/automation\r\nexportPATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:${M2_HOME}/bin:${AUTO_HOME}:$PATH\r\nexportAVID_REPOSITORY=DEV_OES_GUI_1_0\r\nexportBASE_DIR=${WORKSPACE}/oes-gui\r\n \r\nrm -rf${BASE_DIR}\r\ngit clonessh://git@stash.acxiom.com:7999/ib/oes-gui.git\r\ncd${BASE_DIR}\r\ngitcheckout origin/development\r\nBUILD_FILE=rpmbuild.sh\r\nletRELEASE_NUMBER=${BUILD_NUMBER}+2\r\nsed -i -r&quot;s/^RELEASE.+/RELEASE=${RELEASE_NUMBER}/g&quot; ${BUILD_FILE}\r\nsh${BUILD_FILE}\r\ncd${WORKSPACE}\r\n \r\nrm -rf*.rpm\r\nmv `find. -type f -name &quot;*.rpm&quot; | egrep -v \'(\\.src\\.)\' | egrep -v \'BUILD\'` .\r\n \r\nRPM=`ls*.rpm`\r\necho${AVID_USERNAME}\r\npackageService--addPackages --repository ${AVID_REPOSITORY} --packages &quot;${RPM}&quot;</pre><br />\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-08-05 18:33:03', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
	(12, 10, 'OES_GUI_UPGRADE_DEV', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<p style="margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.0pt;" lang="zh-CN"></p><pre class="prettyprint lang-bsh">################SETENVIRONMENT VARIABLE################\r\nexportSOFTWARE_SET=DEV_OES_GUI_1_0_0\r\nexportSERVICE_NAME=OES_DEV_GUI_SERVICE\r\nexportINSTANCES=vm10877.global.shareddev.acxiom.net\r\n \r\ngridService--add-service --service ${SERVICE_NAME} --sw-set ${SOFTWARE_SET} --instance $INSTANCES\r\nsleep 60\r\ngridService--start-service --service ${SERVICE_NAME}</pre><br />\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-08-05 18:34:04', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
	(13, 8, 'git', 'icon-m-file-lock', 'open', 0, 0, '<pre class="prettyprint lang-">1.Clone a repository in Stash\r\ngitclone ssh://git@stash.acxiom.com:7999/flw/flw.git\r\n2.set alias to replace the whole git repository URL\r\n• 1) Enter the cloned gitfolder\r\n• 2) run command:\r\n•git remote add origin ssh://git@stash.acxiom.com:7999/flw/flw.git\r\n•git push origin master\r\nHere, origin is the alias which you can use asthe whole git repository URL\r\n\r\n3. Modify and Check-in modified file\r\n•git status # check files status (Modified-untracked, Staged, Commited)\r\n•\r\n•UseAdd command to make file/folder in Staged status.\r\n•git add filename_or_Foldername # add file/folder which will be in Staged status\r\n•\r\n•Onceall needed files are in Staged status, then could commit them\r\n•Into gitrepository.\r\n•git commit\r\n•An editorial interface will be popedand commit message need to be filled out.\r\n•\r\n•Quickcommit command: use –a and –m option.\r\n•-ameans add the action to Stage not means add file, thus even need to remove afile from Stage, -a still needed.\r\n•git  commit  -a  -m ’added and commited new  files’\r\n•\r\n•Lookup commit history\r\n•git \r\n\r\n4.Branches\r\n•Listall branches\r\n•git branch\r\n•\r\n•Createnew branch\r\n•git branch mybranch\r\n•\r\n•Checkoutbranch\r\n•git checkout mybranch\r\n•\r\n•Mergebranch (merge mybranch to dev branch)\r\n•Aftercommit in mybranch, switch to branch need to bemerged into:\r\n•git checkout dev\r\n•git merge mybranch\r\n•git push origin dev\r\n</pre><br />\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-08-05 23:55:30', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
