	(140, 139, '如何在Tomcat中动态配置', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<p>譬如基于springMVC 框架 web项目, 在tomcat 中动态配置 url 和 文件路径：</p><p>Step 1: Configuration.xml</p><p></p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&gt;\r\n&lt;service desc=&quot;This is an instance of the OES Client Application.&quot;\r\n	name=&quot;OES-GUI&quot;&gt;\r\n	\r\n	&lt;category name=&quot;OES REST Service Configuration&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;string desc=&quot;Service End Point&quot; name=&quot;rest.service.endpoint&quot;\r\n			longdesc=&quot;End Point of OES REST Service&quot; optional=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/string&gt;\r\n			\r\n		&lt;string desc=&quot;Temp Export Path&quot; name=&quot;temp.export.path&quot;\r\n			longdesc=&quot;Temp Export Path For Order Preview Doc&quot; optional=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/string&gt;\r\n			\r\n		&lt;!--&lt;password desc=&quot;OES Password&quot; name=&quot;oes.password&quot;\r\n			longdesc=&quot;OES Mediator Service Password&quot; optional=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/password&gt;  --&gt;\r\n	&lt;/category&gt;\r\n&lt;/service&gt;</pre><br />Step 2: Controller<p></p><p></p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">public class OneController{\r\n\r\n@Value(value = &quot;${temp.export.path}&quot;)\r\nprivate String docPath;\r\n\r\n// Do Something related.\r\n}</pre><p></p><p>Step 3: 在Tomcat中配置：<br /></p><p></p><div><img src="file:///C:\\Users\\wewang.AP\\AppData\\Roaming\\Tencent\\Users\\841736591\\QQ\\WinTemp\\RichOle\\8QG3[J1]N]0@9}SVQHDUS17.jpg" alt="" /><img src="static/xheditor-1.2.1/xheditor_plugins/upload/files/day_141017/201410171710025129.jpg" alt="" /></div><br /><p></p><p>Step 4： 重新启动Tomcat, OK.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>#### &nbsp;更新 2014年10月23日16:53:23 ######</strong></p><p><strong>Step 1： 在AccountServiceImpl.java类中:</strong></p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">public class AccountServiceImpl implements AccountService {\r\n\r\n	private String endPoint; //定义\r\n\r\n//使用\r\n	public LoginResponse loginUser(LoginCredential loginAccount) throws OesException{\r\n		LoginResponse loginResponse = new LoginResponse();\r\n		RestTemplate restTemplate = new RestTemplate();\r\n		String encPassword = CipherEncrypter.encode(loginAccount.getPassword());\r\n		String url = this.endPoint + &quot;user/login?&quot; + &quot;userName=&quot; + loginAccount.getUsername() + &quot;&amp;password=&quot;\r\n				+ encPassword;\r\n		try{\r\n			loginResponse = restTemplate.getForObject(url, LoginResponse.class);\r\n			return loginResponse;\r\n		} catch (Exception e){\r\n			throw ExceptionBuilder.buildOesException(ErrorCodeConstant.LOGIN_SERVICE_NOT_AVAIL, null);\r\n		}\r\n	}\r\n	public String getEndPoint() {\r\n		return endPoint;\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	public void setEndPoint(String endPoint) {\r\n		this.endPoint = endPoint;\r\n	}\r\n}</pre><br /><br /></p><p><strong>Step 2：dispatcher-servlet.xml文件中</strong></p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">	&lt;bean id=&quot;accountService&quot; class=&quot;com.acxiom.oes.service.impl.AccountServiceImpl&quot; &gt;\r\n		&lt;property name=&quot;endPoint&quot; value=&quot;${rest.service.endpoint}&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\r\n	&lt;/bean&gt;	</pre><br /><strong>Step 3: &nbsp;Tomcat中填入Environment的键值对</strong></p><p><img src="http://www.minws.com/codepad/static/xheditor-1.2.1/xheditor_plugins/upload/files/day_141017/201410171710025129.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /></p><p><br /></p>\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-10-17 17:11:36', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
