	(155, 204, '20141023-sprint6-template', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<p><strong>20141023-sprint6-template</strong></p><p>VB source code--- ucStartOrder.ctl (页面的入口处)</p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">ucStartOrder.ctl \r\nPrivate Sub UpdateLabels_ScreenComps()\r\n--用于更新page上的label名\r\n\r\nPrivate Sub btnOpen_Click()\r\n--open click\r\n\r\nPrivate Sub btnNew_Click()\r\n--new click\r\n\r\n\r\n.bas 和 .ctl 并用，在ctl里找不到的变量，可以到.bas中查找\r\n例如StartOrder.bas 和ucStartOrder.ctl 并用。\r\n\r\n\r\nPublic g_objOrder           As oesOrder_r10_0_0_4.CoesOrders\r\nBegin VB.OptionButton rbTemplates\r\nBegin VB.OptionButton rbOrders\r\n\r\n\r\nPrivate Sub rbTemplates_Click()\r\n  On Error GoTo ErrorRoutine\r\n\r\n  If g_bOption2_Displayed Then\r\n    Disable_For_Template_Selection\r\n  End If\r\n\r\n/* order click*/\r\nPrivate Sub rbOrders_Click()\r\n  On Error GoTo ErrorRoutine\r\n\r\n  If g_bOption2_Displayed Then\r\n    Enable_For_Order_Selection\r\n  End If</pre><strong></strong></p><p><strong><br /></strong></p>##### oes-gui ######<p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">changeTab($event)\r\n\r\n$scope.changeTab = function(clickEvent){\r\n\r\n很多ucStartorder.ctl中会使用到 Me.IsTemplate = bIsTemplate\r\n    mStartOrder.IsTemplate = Me.IsTemplate 这里的mStartOrder指的是StartOrder.bas中的\r\nAttribute VB_Name = &quot;mStartOrder&quot; \r\n\r\n\r\n&gt; 1. ucStartOrder.ctl 中，\r\n\r\n[#A]...  line 1075 说道： \r\n  \'If an order is found in the temp table with the current user\'s userid\r\n  \'then inform the user that they will be re-attached to the open order.\r\n即要判断当前的user是否在临时表t_oesOrder中有Orderinfo,若有，那么页面提示，并且后台要返回ORderInfo\r\n----&gt; 返回的Order赋值给当前的页面属性，\r\n（1）类似 line 1102 那段：Me.OrderNumber = g_rsOrders(&quot;OrderNumber&quot;)\r\n    mStartOrder.OrderNumber = Me.OrderNumber\r\n   ... mStartOrder.IsTemplate = Me.IsTemplate 等等\r\n（2） 还有 line 1113 中 If g_rsOrders(&quot;StagedOrder&quot;) = &quot;Y&quot;；\r\n（3）line 1119 check Global Customer： if CustomerID = (“###########”)，then CustomerName = &quot;Global&quot;; else if admin, then &quot;tsStdCustName&quot;\r\n（4）getCustomers, \r\nMsgBox &quot;You currently have &quot; &amp; IIf(Me.IsTemplate, &quot;template&quot;, &quot;order&quot;) &amp; _\r\n           &quot; &quot; &amp; mStartOrder.OrderNumber &amp; &quot; in edit mode.  It will now be recovered.&quot;, _\r\n           vbOKOnly, &quot;Locked &quot; &amp; IIf(Me.IsTemplate, &quot;Template&quot;, &quot;Order&quot;) &amp; &quot; Found&quot;\r\n （5）RaiseEvent GoToOrderDetailsURL 跳转到OrderDetails页面\r\n// 第五点个人理解为：若判断当前用户的临时表Order信息正好是Order的，则跳转Order；若不是，是Template的，则跳转到Template;\r\n[#B]... line 1180 更新当前的页面\r\n\'update labels and screen comps for Orders/Templates \r\n  UpdateLabels_ScreenComps\r\nline 1233 主要更新页面上的 Start ** 和 Open ** , **以 Order 和Template 代替\r\n\r\n   Begin VB.Label lblInstruct_New \r\n      AutoSize        =   -1  \'True\r\n      BackStyle       =   0  \'Transparent\r\n      Caption         =   &quot;Create a new &quot;\r\n\r\n   Begin VB.Label lblInstruct_Open \r\n      AutoSize        =   -1  \'True\r\n      BackStyle       =   0  \'Transparent\r\n      Caption         =   &quot;Open an &quot;\r\n\r\n\r\n[#C] line 1182 写道\'get the all the customers\r\n  PopulateCustomers\r\nline 486 Private Sub PopulateCustomers()\r\n... 增加 Global的Customer， 增加 TS Standard Customer\r\n将getCustomers以若有number存在的，则将其加在中间，name-number-Id 格式\r\n\r\n\r\n最后\r\n[#D] line 1187 写道 If (Me.IsTemplate = False) And (Me.CustomerID = String(13, &quot;#&quot;)) Then \r\n	这条if语句显然是有问题的啊？？？？\r\n</pre><br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-12-15 16:32:20', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
	(156, 204, '20141024-sprint6-template', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<p><strong>20141024-sprint6-template</strong></p><p>oes java代码:</p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">#1. 1  var LABEL_ARRAY = [{  //定义了selection criteria 这个对话框里的针对Order或是Template的分别三种（Open，Copy，Stage）一共六种情况组成的数组\r\n{\r\n  option1Label: \'Option 1: Open a specific order\',\r\n  templateOrderNumberLabel:\'Order Number:\',\r\n  option2Label:\'Option 2: Enter selection criteria for a list of available orders to open\',\r\n  productShow: false,\r\n  ordersOptionShow: true,\r\n  templatesOptionShow: false\r\n},\r\n\r\nTODo： 确认下Template下productShow//ordersOptionShow//templatesOptionShow 的值是否正确？\r\n\r\noes-service.js中\r\noesServicesApp.factory(\'OrderSelectionService\',[\'$rootScope\',\'$http\', function($rootScope, $http){\r\nvar showOpenTemplateSelectionCriteria = function () {\r\n	showSelectionCriteria(3, 2, false, false,  0, 0);\r\n};\r\n\r\nfunction showSelectionCriteria(i, p, oeo, oco, con, cov){}\r\n	var input = {\r\n			index : i,\r\n			processType : p, // 指的是“open copy stage三者之一”\r\n			onlyElementOrders : oeo, // 1\r\n			onlyComponentOrders : oco, // 2\r\n			tsAdminUser : tsAdminUser,\r\n			currOrderNumber : con,\r\n			currOrderVersion : cov,\r\n			tsStdCustID : tsStandardCustId,// 3\r\n			restEndPoint : restEndPoint// 4 以上四个参数只有在Import Element才会用到的，所以其他情况都会设置为FALSE.\r\n		};\r\n\r\n调用： 在start-order.controller.js中\r\n  	$scope.openOrder = function(){\r\n  		if($scope.order == null){\r\n  			orderSelectionService.showOpenOrderSelectionCriteria();  //此处调用\r\n  		}else{\r\n  			//Synchronized\r\n  			if(orderService.isUpgradeNeeded($scope.order)){\r\n  				//TODO: prompt for upgrade service\r\n  				orderService.upgradeOrder($scope.order);\r\n  			}else{\r\n  				order = orderService.openOrder($scope.order);\r\n  				//redirect to order details page\r\n  			}\r\n  		}\r\n  	};\r\n</pre><br />#1.2&nbsp;<br /></p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">jS文件 : oes-service.js\r\nvar oesServicesApp = angular.module(\'oesServicesApp\', []);\r\n\r\njS文件 : order.app.js\r\nvar orderApp = angular.module(\'orderApp\',[\'oesServicesApp\']);\r\n* orderApp is the whole module of order pages.\r\n * Include this file after oes services.\r\n\r\n页面start-order.jsp  &amp; order-details.jsp &amp; order-eements,jsp &amp; finalize-order.jsp\r\n&lt;html ng-app=&quot;orderApp&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;acxiom-page-container&quot; id=&quot;start-order&quot; ng-controller=&quot;StartOrderController&quot;&gt;\r\n在html标签注明ng-app=&quot;orderApp&quot;，并且在body标签注明了一个controller “StartOrderController”\r\n\r\n通过ng-app，ng-controller 则可找到 start-order.controller.js中\r\norderApp.controller(\'StartOrderController\',[\r\n</pre><br />#2：</p><p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">##################################################\r\n\r\n#2. need to write a openTemplate 方法, 模拟openOrder 方法（oes-order.service.js , line + 45）\r\n	/**\r\n	 * open an existing order.\r\n	 */\r\n	var openOrder = function(order){\r\n		var url = \'/order/open.spring\';\r\n				data = {\r\n					&quot;orderNumber&quot; : order.orderNumber,\r\n					&quot;orderVersion&quot; : order.orderVersion,\r\n					&quot;versionType&quot; : order.versionType,\r\n					&quot;customerId&quot; : order.customerId\r\n				};\r\n		$http({\r\n			 method: \'POST\', \r\n			 url: commonService.getGuiUrl(url), \r\n			 cache: false,\r\n			 data : data,\r\n			 dataType : &quot;json&quot;,\r\n			 contentType : \'application/json\',\r\n			 }).success(function(response, status) {\r\n				 document.location.href= commonService.getGuiUrl(&quot;/order/open-order-detail.spring&quot;);\r\n	   	}).error(function(response, status) {\r\n	    if(data.error){\r\n	    	// TODO: Show error messages.\r\n	    }\r\n	   });\r\n	};\r\n\r\n//GuiUrl\r\nvar getGuiUrl = function(path){\r\n	return path ? GLOBAL_CONTEXT + path : GLOBAL_CONTEXT;\r\n};\r\n\r\n1. $rootScope\r\n2. $scope\r\n3. *.jsp : &lt;select id=&quot;customerSelect&quot; ng-model=&quot;customerSelect&quot;\r\nng-model: 可以到*.controller.js中查找\r\n\r\n*.js : var currentCustomer = customerService.getCurrentCustomer();\r\n		if (currentCustomer) {\r\n			$scope.customerSelect = currentCustomer.customerId;\r\n		}\r\n\r\n4. ucStartOrder.ctl\r\n+709\r\n\'show the Blank,Orders,Templates and open the chosen order number\r\n  ShowSelections_OpenOrderTemplate False</pre><br /><br /></p>\r\n', 'wengel', '2014-12-15 16:31:43', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
	(157, 204, '20141025-sprint6-template', 'icon-m-file', 'open', 0, 1, '<p><strong>20141025-sprint6-template</strong></p><p><strong>翻译的java代码记录:</strong></p><p></p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">jsp:  &lt;div class=&quot;acxiom-page-container&quot; id=&quot;start-order&quot; ng-controller=&quot;StartOrderController&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; id=&quot;currentPage&quot; value=&quot;subnav-start-order&quot;&gt; \r\n\r\n对应navigation.controller.js\r\nvar routes = {\r\n	\'startOrder\' :  {\r\n		div:&quot;start-order&quot;,\r\n		link : commonService.getGuiUrl(\'/order/start-order.spring\')\r\n	},\r\n	\'orderDetail\' : {\r\n		div : &quot;order-detail&quot;,\r\n		link : commonService.getGuiUrl(\'/order/open-order-detail.spring\') \r\n	},\r\n}\r\n\r\n//current page =&gt; store event\r\nvar events = {\r\n	&quot;subnav-start-order&quot;:{\r\n		event:&quot;START-ORDER&quot;,\r\n		on:&quot;START-ORDER-END&quot;\r\n	},\r\n	&quot;subnav-order-details&quot; : {\r\n		event : &quot;STORE_ORDER_DETAILS&quot;,\r\n		on : &quot;STORE_ORDER_DETAILS_END&quot;\r\n	},\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * init customer session\r\n */\r\n$scope.initSelectItems = function() {</pre><p></p><p><br /></p><strong>遇到的问题记录：</strong><p></p><pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">#1. 部署成功后，Navigation tab不跳转到指定页面，原因是：navigation.tag里的li里少写了个参数，ng-click=&quot;处理&quot;\r\n&lt;li data-tab-id=&quot;subnav-start-template&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;startTemplate&quot; ng-click=&quot;changeTab($event)&quot;&gt;Start Template&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n#2. Angularjs部署Unknown provider: aProvider &lt;- a\r\nError: [$injector:unpr] Unknown provider: TemplateServiceProvider &lt;- TemplateService\r\nhttp://errors.angularjs.org/1.2.21/$injector/unpr?p0=TemplateServiceProvider%20%3C-%20TemplateService\r\n错误与原因是：oes-angular-common.tag 缺少了&lt;script src=&quot;${ctx}/resources/js/oes/services/oes-template.service.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; 的引入：\r\n&lt;%@ taglib p