	(215, 39, '20150114-Tom-Exe', 'icon-m-file-lock', 'open', 0, 0, '<pre class="prettyprint linenums lang-js">package com.acxiom.java.study;\r\n\r\npublic class L0114_JavaLoader {\r\n\r\n       private static int count = 0;\r\n       \r\n       static String cn = print(count());\r\n       \r\n       String cn2 = print(count());\r\n       \r\n       static {\r\n              print(&quot;静态块&quot;);\r\n       }\r\n       \r\n       static String cn3 = print(count());\r\n       \r\n       String cn4 = print(count());\r\n       \r\n       public L0114_JavaLoader() {\r\n              print(count());\r\n              print(&quot;构造器&quot;);\r\n       }\r\n       \r\n       public L0114_JavaLoader(String name) {\r\n              super();\r\n              print(name);\r\n       }\r\n       /**\r\n       * @param args\r\n       */\r\n       public static void main(String[] args) {\r\n              new L0114_JavaLoader();\r\n              new L0114_JavaLoader(&quot;TOMMY&quot;);\r\n              new L0114_JavaLoader(&quot;HARVEY&quot;);\r\n       }\r\n\r\n       public static String count() {\r\n              count ++;\r\n              return &quot;&quot; + count;\r\n       }\r\n       \r\n       public static String print(String input) {\r\n              System.out.println(input);\r\n              return input;\r\n       }\r\n}\r\n\r\n</pre><br />把上面的代码copy到你们的eclipse里面跑跑看， 看结果，然后分析一下java的load机制，明天下午5点我会出点考题，然后再讲其他的java基础知识。\r\n', 'wengel', '2015-01-14 18:13:35', '', '2015-08-14 15:12:49'),
